@@aCLERIC@@W

Clerics are keepers of sacred covenant, shaping divine force through faith and
rite. They stand between ruin and renewal, turning conviction into miracles.

@@aPassive class abilities@@W
  * @@wSpell Critical Damage@@W (unlocked at mortal level 20): increases
    spell critical multiplier by @@w2 x Wisdom@@W.

@@aUnique Cleric mechanics@@W
  * Prime mortal attribute is @@wWisdom@@W.
  * Excels at high-impact spell spikes when criticals land, making Cleric a
    strong base for holy and support-caster progressions.

@@aCleric reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * Every @@w2 Cleric reincarnations@@W (rounded up) increases max
    @@wWisdom@@W by 1.
  * At @@w1+ Cleric reincarnation@@W, @@wSpell Critical Damage@@W is
    permanently unlocked for all future class paths.

